description: In one transaction, she was pregnant with an unfamiliar child. She was pregnant and married to a man who was bound to have a baby. I thought it was a transaction with their own minds at this time, but in this marriage, I entangled with affection that shouldn't be there. When she was pregnant in October, she woke up with a divorce agreement on the ground.>
